characterDescription.skinTone: fair skin with subtle pink undertones, especially noticeable on cheeks and forehead. Even complexion with minimal visible blemishes.
characterDescription.eyeColor: light sky blue eyes with a slightly darker limbal ring around the iris. There are barely visible lighter almost grayish-white specks in the iris itself. Eyes are very vibrant.
characterDescription.eyeShape: almond-shaped eyes, with a slight downward tilt at the outer corners, giving a gentle expression. The upper eyelid has a subtle fold and the lower eyelid appears slightly puffy.
characterDescription.hairColor: dark auburn-brown hair with natural lighter highlights that catch the light. The roots appear slightly darker, indicating a richer, deeper brown.
characterDescription.hairTexture: fine, slightly wavy hair with soft, loose curls particularly around the face. The overall density appears medium.
characterDescription.hairStyle: hair is styled into two high pigtail buns on top of the head, secured with pink alligator clips adorned with small white pom-poms. Some loose strands frame the face, creating a slightly messy, playful look.
characterDescription.faceShape: oval face with a rounded forehead and soft, slightly chubby cheeks. The jawline is soft and not particularly defined.
characterDescription.nose: small, delicate nose with a slightly upturned tip. The bridge is straight and narrow, fitting proportionally with the rest of the face.
characterDescription.lips: naturally pink lips, with a slightly fuller bottom lip than top lip. The mouth is small and well-defined, giving a sweet expression.
characterDescription.smile: no visible smile, but the lips are slightly pursed, creating a thoughtful expression. The teeth are not visible.
characterDescription.eyebrows: medium-thick eyebrows, slightly darker than the hair color. They have a naturally arched shape and are well-groomed.
characterDescription.ears: visible left ear is medium-sized and set close to the head. The lobe is attached.
characterDescription.cheeks: full, rounded cheeks with a slight rosiness, giving a youthful appearance. The cheeks are prominent and contribute to the overall sweetness of the face.
characterDescription.chin: rounded, soft chin that blends seamlessly into the jawline. It is neither pointed nor particularly prominent.
characterDescription.facialProportions: balanced facial proportions, with eyes taking up a significant portion of the upper face. The nose is small relative to the rest of the face, and the mouth is proportionately sized.
characterDescription.distinctiveFeatures: subtle, very light freckles are barely visible across the bridge of the nose. The slight puffiness under the eyes adds to the youthful appearance. The overall look conveys innocence and a touch of seriousness.
characterDescription.overallImpression: a sweet and innocent child with a slightly serious expression. The light blue eyes and auburn hair create a striking contrast. Her overall appearance is charming and endearing.
characterDescription.fullDescription: This child is a 5-6 year old girl with fair skin and subtle pink undertones, most noticeable on her cheeks. Her light sky blue eyes, with their dark limbal rings, are almond-shaped and slightly downturned at the corners. Her dark auburn-brown hair is styled in two high pigtail buns with pink pom-pom clips, framing her oval face with its soft, slightly chubby cheeks. Her small, delicate nose has a slightly upturned tip, and her naturally pink lips are slightly pursed in a thoughtful expression. With her barely visible freckles across her nose bridge and a slight puffiness under her eyes, her features combine to give her a sweet, innocent, and slightly serious appearance.
